    AclfBus, AcscBus, BaseAclfBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseDStabBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseOpfBus, BaseOpfGenBus, DclfOpfBus, DclfOpfGenBus, DStabBus, Dynamic3PBus, OpfBus, OpfGenBus, Steady3PBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAclfBus, AclfBusImpl, AcscBusImpl, BaseAclfBusImpl, BaseAcscBusImpl, BaseDStabBusImpl, BaseOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfGenBusImpl, DStabBusImpl, Dynamic3PBusImpl, OpfBusImpl, OpfGenBusImpl, Steady3PBusImpl

    public interface IAclfBus
    A representation of the model object 'Base Aclf Bus'. interface to implment AclfBus as an extension.
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getIAclfBus()
